{{Lunisolar October}} '''October 30''' is the 30th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=Kannazuki|1=Kannazuki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
As with all other days 30 of the Sino-Japanese calendar it sometimes happens and sometimes does not depending on the lunar cycle.<ref>https://www.ndl.go.jp/koyomi/e/history/index.html</ref>Months are also annotated as either long ({{zh|c=大|l=big}} for months with 30 days) or short ({{zh|c=小|l=small}} for months with 29 days). There are also other elements of the traditional Chinese calendar.<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20250111081847/https://www.chinaknowledge.de/History/Terms/calendar.html</ref><ref>https://www.nippon.com/en/japan-glances/jg00122/the-japanese-calendar.html</ref>
== Events ==
== Births == * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1596|ja|1596|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 19|ja|12月19日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Matsudaira Nobutsuna|ja|松平信綱|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Edo Shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Rōchū|ja|老中|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} （+ {{ill|1662|ja|1662|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） * {{ill|Kangxi|ja|Kangxi|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 17th year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1678|ja|1678|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 3|ja|12月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Emperor Yongzheng|ja|雍正帝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Qing dynasty|ja|清|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} の5代{{ill|Emperor|ja|Emperor|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} （+ {{ill|1735|ja|1735|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ）
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenshō (Japan)|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 12nd year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1584|ja|1584|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 8|ja|11月8日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Ashina Moritaka|ja|蘆名盛隆|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Sengoku daimyo|ja|戦国大名|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1561|ja|1561|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) * {{ill|Shōtoku (era)|ja|正徳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1715|ja|1715|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Shibukawa Harumi|ja|渋川春海|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , also known as the 2nd {{ill|Yasui Santetsu|ja|安井算哲|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , astronomer and calendrical scholar (* {{ill|1639|ja|1639|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) * {{ill|Enkyō (Japan)|ja|Enkyō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1747|ja|1747|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 8|ja|11月8日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Terazaka Nobuyuki|ja|寺坂信行|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , one of the {{ill|Forty-seven rōnin|ja|赤穂浪士|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1665|ja|1665|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) == Commemorations ==
